			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1985427">
									

<p>As you probably gathered, new contest! Thanks very much to staff in general for helping refine this contest, Dexanote in particular for refining the original idea and Aelanna for helping with the technical side of the contest <span style="text-decoration: line-through;">and not drawing attention to the fact that I misspelled &quot;appreciated&quot; in the title</span>!</p>
<p>I want to also take this opportunity to preemptively thank the individuals who enter this contest, because this contest is important to me. We have so many overlooked articles, so many great SCPs that are just simply not as visible among the thousands of articles we have in this list, so by entering this contest and helping bring visibility to these diamonds in the rough, you're helping the site culture as a whole by widening the community's knowledge base, and that means a lot, it really does.</p>
<p>Enough sappy stuff, though, let's get this contest underway!</p>

